371
00:20:19,980 --> 00:20:22,080
When I wrote this letter of commitment,

372
00:20:22,080 --> 00:20:22,750
I didn't know

373
00:20:22,750 --> 00:20:24,090
that Shangyu was my childhood friend.

374
00:20:24,090 --> 00:20:26,540
