375
00:20:26,540 --> 00:20:28,650
Is he not a man or are you not a woman?

376
00:20:30,850 --> 00:20:31,910
Didn't you promise

377
00:20:31,910 --> 00:20:34,170
to return the letter of commitment to me?

378
00:20:35,250 --> 00:20:36,250
Give it back to me.

379
00:20:38,610 --> 00:20:40,470
I was planning to return it to you,

380
00:20:40,910 --> 00:20:41,450
but I didn't expect

381
00:20:41,450 --> 00:20:43,440
