384
00:20:47,010 --> 00:20:50,260
I'll keep this letter of commitment for now.

385
00:20:53,780 --> 00:20:54,660
Scoundrel.

386
00:20:56,690 --> 00:20:57,740
Say that again.

387
00:20:57,790 --> 00:20:59,640
You really are a scoundrel.

388
00:21:02,050 --> 00:21:02,890
Xiaoqi.

389
00:21:02,920 --> 00:21:04,950
House rule number 18:

390
00:21:05,710 --> 00:21:08,960
Anyone who defies or insults the Young Lord

391
00:21:09,750 --> 00:21:11,810
shall receive 50 strokes of the cane.

392
00:21:13,890 --> 00:21:15,350
Did you hear that clearly?

393
00:21:17,190 --> 00:21:17,870
Xiaoqi.

394
00:21:18,710 --> 00:21:21,310
Have someone prepare some late-night snacks.

395
00:21:21,430 --> 00:21:22,780
The night is young.

396
00:21:22,820 --> 00:21:24,500
I should savor it slowly.

397
00:21:25,350 --> 00:21:25,910
Yes.

398
00:21:30,350 --> 00:21:31,680
What are you still waiting for?

399
00:21:31,680 --> 00:21:32,520
Begin.

400
00:21:35,030 --> 00:21:36,370
Alright.

401
00:21:44,950 --> 00:21:46,630
Since you're so eager to hear

402
00:21:46,650 --> 00:21:48,130
and watch a good show,

403
00:21:48,510 --> 00:21:50,030
I'll perform for you the story

404
00:21:50,030 --> 00:21:54,470
of a shameless Young Lord forcibly taking a charming commoner girl.

405
00:21:58,500 --> 00:21:59,230
How's that?

406
00:22:00,510 --> 00:22:01,310
Begin.

407
00:22:06,840 --> 00:22:09,170
Why is he pretending to be so magnanimous?

408
00:22:09,310 --> 00:22:11,390
Let's see how long you can endure.

409
00:22:16,030 --> 00:22:19,200
Once upon a time, there was a Young Lord

410
00:22:19,320 --> 00:22:22,160
called the Shameless Young Lord.

411
00:22:22,350 --> 00:22:25,180
He thought himself as handsome as a celestial being,

412
00:22:25,180 --> 00:22:27,030
but he was quite pitiful.

413
00:22:27,030 --> 00:22:28,950
He had never looked in a mirror,

414
00:22:29,020 --> 00:22:31,620
and no one dared to tell him

415
00:22:31,790 --> 00:22:36,110
that he was actually extremely ugly.

416
00:22:42,970 --> 00:22:44,130
Why are you looking at me?

417
00:22:44,130 --> 00:22:45,130
Go on.

418
00:22:49,510 --> 00:22:52,630
If you dare to watch, I dare to perform.

419
00:22:54,360 --> 00:22:57,810
This ugly Young Lord is not only hideous,

420
00:22:58,020 --> 00:22:59,650
but he also stinks terribly.

421
00:23:00,020 --> 00:23:02,560
He has to bathe eight times a day.

422
00:23:03,270 --> 00:23:05,470
But no matter how many times he bathes,

423
00:23:05,470 --> 00:23:07,230
he still stinks.

424
00:23:07,430 --> 00:23:09,760
Because he's not only physically smelly,

425
00:23:09,770 --> 00:23:12,620
his nature and his temper stink too.

426
00:23:14,690 --> 00:23:15,920
One day,

427
00:23:16,030 --> 00:23:19,890
a charming commoner girl was happily walking down the street.

428
00:23:20,040 --> 00:23:23,400
Suddenly, she encountered this shameless Young Lord.

429
00:23:23,430 --> 00:23:25,710
This shameless Young Lord

430
00:23:25,710 --> 00:23:26,910
