431
00:23:26,910 --> 00:23:28,910
The girl cried, 'Help! Help! Help!'

432
00:23:28,910 --> 00:23:30,060
Stop chasing me!

433
00:23:32,100 --> 00:23:33,550
The performance was quite enthusiastic.

434
00:23:33,550 --> 00:23:35,430
Run, run!

435
00:23:35,580 --> 00:23:37,810
It looks like a supernatural tale.

436
00:23:38,300 --> 00:23:40,960
Could it be a mountain demon abducting a beauty?

437
00:23:41,840 --> 00:23:45,300
The shameless Young Lord is still chasing her,

438
00:23:45,860 --> 00:23:47,660
keeping on chasing and chasing.

439
00:24:03,630 --> 00:24:05,990
This little devil tormented me all night.

440
00:24:06,010 --> 00:24:07,740
Now my arms are so sore.

441
00:24:08,910 --> 00:24:10,510
I've insulted him so much,

442
00:24:11,310 --> 00:24:13,620
yet he still seems quite happy.

443
00:24:14,440 --> 00:24:15,630
He's really thick-skinned

444
00:24:15,630 --> 00:24:16,790
and shameless.

445
00:24:23,830 --> 00:24:24,510
Fei.

446
00:24:26,230 --> 00:24:27,070
Shangyu.

447
00:24:27,670 --> 00:24:28,530
Come, sit down.

448
00:24:30,550 --> 00:24:31,270
Have one.

449
00:24:33,470 --> 00:24:34,800
I don't like to eat that.

450
00:24:35,530 --> 00:24:37,250
You've really changed.

451
00:24:37,280 --> 00:24:39,150
You used to eat whatever I gave you.

452
00:24:39,150 --> 00:24:39,910
I was afraid that one day,

453
00:24:39,910 --> 00:24:41,190
you might eat me too.

454
00:24:41,920 --> 00:24:43,610
It's not that exaggerated.

455
00:24:46,230 --> 00:24:49,030
Did the Young Lord give you any trouble yesterday?

456
00:24:52,290 --> 00:24:55,510
How could he dare to trouble me?

457
00:24:56,480 --> 00:24:57,480
That's good then.

458
00:24:57,720 --> 00:25:00,100
If the Young Lord doesn't treat you well,

459
00:25:00,610 --> 00:25:02,140
I can take you away anytime.

460
00:25:02,280 --> 00:25:03,360
No, that won't do.

461
00:25:03,400 --> 00:25:06,060
I still have to stay here and be his entertainer.

462
00:25:07,360 --> 00:25:09,010
Are you that eager to be an entertainer?

463
00:25:09,010 --> 00:25:10,890
It's not that I want to.

464
00:25:11,030 --> 00:25:11,950
It's just...

465
00:25:15,520 --> 00:25:17,150
I called out to you several times from up there.

466
00:25:17,150 --> 00:25:18,230
Didn't you hear me?

467
00:25:22,000 --> 00:25:22,800
Wait a minute.

468
00:25:23,110 --> 00:25:24,240
Something's wrong.

469
00:25:24,640 --> 00:25:25,590
What's wrong?

470
00:25:28,290 --> 00:25:32,780
He's actually an utterly hideous freak.

471
00:25:36,910 --> 00:25:38,070
Why are you looking at me?

472
00:25:38,070 --> 00:25:38,890
Go on.

473
00:25:40,080 --> 00:25:41,360
Something's off.

474
00:25:41,510 --> 00:25:43,170
Something's definitely off.

475
00:25:44,040 --> 00:25:46,190
Before, when I said anything bad about him,

476
00:25:46,190 --> 00:25:48,450
he would react like I stepped on his tail.

477
00:25:48,830 --> 00:25:50,350
Yesterday I insulted him all night,

478
00:25:50,350 --> 00:25:52,310
yet he didn't react at all.

479
00:25:53,810 --> 00:25:55,630
I need to figure this out.

480
00:25:56,150 --> 00:25:57,110
Ruofei.

481
00:25:58,230 --> 00:25:59,030
What's wrong?

482
00:25:59,590 --> 00:26:00,960
Something crossed my mind.

483
00:26:00,960 --> 00:26:01,820
I have to go now.

484
00:26:18,820 --> 00:26:20,390
As I thought, he can't hear.

485
00:26:33,480 --> 00:26:36,780
Your petty tricks won't scare me.

486
00:26:37,270 --> 00:26:38,600
How childish.

487
00:26:45,860 --> 00:26:47,260
What are you trying to do?

488
00:26:48,080 --> 00:26:49,460
Still not letting go?

489
00:27:04,860 --> 00:27:05,630
Damn it.

490
00:27:05,630 --> 00:27:07,110
He tricked me again.

491
00:27:09,260 --> 00:27:10,320
Could it be that...

492
00:27:11,110 --> 00:27:12,470
I'm overthinking it?

493
00:27:35,190 --> 00:27:37,150
I understand now.

494
00:27:38,470 --> 00:27:41,030
So all these mirrors in the mansion

495
00:27:41,330 --> 00:27:44,120
aren't just for vanity.

496
00:27:50,230 --> 00:27:52,630
Oh, you little devil.

497
00:27:53,790 --> 00:27:55,710
Looks like you finally have a flaw

498
00:27:55,710 --> 00:27:58,000
that I can take advantage of.

499
00:27:58,150 --> 00:27:59,990
I must get to the bottom of this.

500
00:28:01,820 --> 00:28:02,640
Shanshan.

501
00:28:03,260 --> 00:28:03,910
Shanshan.

502
00:28:04,750 --> 00:28:05,710
Come here and take a look.

503
00:28:05,710 --> 00:28:07,370
See what I've brought for you.

504
00:28:10,440 --> 00:28:11,360
Shanshan.

505
00:28:13,990 --> 00:28:14,720
Shanshan.

506
00:28:17,750 --> 00:28:18,430
Shanshan.

507
00:28:19,120 --> 00:28:20,520
How have you been lately?

508
00:28:21,450 --> 00:28:22,890
Greetings, Mayor.

509
00:28:25,030 --> 00:28:26,900
Did I interrupt your practice?

510
00:28:27,060 --> 00:28:28,040
It's my fault.

511
00:28:28,230 --> 00:28:29,600
I'll be more careful next time.

512
00:28:29,600 --> 00:28:31,190
Come here.

513
00:28:31,210 --> 00:28:32,330
Come over and take a look.

514
00:28:32,330 --> 00:28:34,460
I've brought you lots of delicious treats.

515
00:28:34,460 --> 00:28:35,340
Come on.

516
00:28:41,350 --> 00:28:42,160
Here.

517
00:28:43,720 --> 00:28:45,720
I'd searched all over Symphony City

518
00:28:45,830 --> 00:28:46,870
before I found these.

519
00:28:46,870 --> 00:28:48,870
Your favorite Cloud City's snacks.

520
00:28:48,950 --> 00:28:49,610
Come on.

521
00:28:49,670 --> 00:28:51,770
Try them and see if they suit your taste.

522
00:28:51,770 --> 00:28:52,350
Come here.

523
00:28:52,350 --> 00:28:53,820
Sit down.

524
00:28:56,830 --> 00:28:58,630
If the food here doesn't suit your taste,

525
00:28:58,630 --> 00:28:59,560
just let me know.

526
00:28:59,570 --> 00:29:01,770
I'll bring a chef from Cloud City later.

527
00:29:03,150 --> 00:29:03,850
Oh yeah.

528
00:29:04,100 --> 00:29:04,830
Huang Fu.

529
00:29:04,870 --> 00:29:05,910
Come in.

530
00:29:09,190 --> 00:29:10,250
Here.

531
00:29:11,000 --> 00:29:12,290
Open it.

532
00:29:12,840 --> 00:29:15,760
These are all popular accessories in Symphony City.

533
00:29:15,760 --> 00:29:17,400
I'm not sure what you like,

534
00:29:17,420 --> 00:29:19,260
so I've bought out several of the best shops

535
00:29:19,260 --> 00:29:20,430
in Symphony City.

536
00:29:20,550 --> 00:29:22,810
You can go and choose for yourself later.

537
00:29:23,430 --> 00:29:24,950
Here, take a look at these.

538
00:29:26,630 --> 00:29:27,890
See if you like them.

539
00:29:28,400 --> 00:29:29,370
Don't worry.

540
00:29:29,570 --> 00:29:30,720
As long as I'm here,

541
00:29:30,970 --> 00:29:32,430
when it comes to food, drink, and clothing,

542
00:29:32,430 --> 00:29:34,640
I won't let you be inferior to any other musician.

543
00:29:34,640 --> 00:29:35,410
Mayor.

544
00:29:35,630 --> 00:29:38,190
I came here to study the art of music.

545
00:29:38,500 --> 00:29:40,290
We don't lack anything here.

546
00:29:40,510 --> 00:29:41,870
Please don't spend any more money.

547
00:29:41,870 --> 00:29:42,710
Fine.

548
00:29:42,710 --> 00:29:43,790
I understand.

549
00:29:46,880 --> 00:29:49,810
Look at this beautiful sunny day.

550
00:29:50,180 --> 00:29:53,420
I've heard that Jiuyu Mountain outside the city has beautiful scenery.

551
00:29:53,420 --> 00:29:56,300
Why don't we go enjoy the spring scenery together?

552
00:29:56,350 --> 00:29:57,010
No, thanks.

553
00:29:57,290 --> 00:29:59,730
I want to practice as much as I can now.

554
00:29:59,760 --> 00:30:01,130
If I can't be the best,

555
00:30:01,390 --> 00:30:02,780
it's a failure for me.

556
00:30:06,400 --> 00:30:06,990
Alright.

557
00:30:07,640 --> 00:30:08,970
So you want to practice.

558
00:30:10,210 --> 00:30:12,400
What should I do with my day then?

559
00:30:15,090 --> 00:30:16,830
Isn't that the harp I gave you?

560
00:30:19,280 --> 00:30:21,500
I'm very attached to that harp.

561
00:30:21,610 --> 00:30:23,150
From Cloud City to Symphony City,

562
00:30:23,150 --> 00:30:25,480
I've kept the harp with me the entire time.

563
00:30:26,360 --> 00:30:27,960
If you have nothing else to do,

564
00:30:27,960 --> 00:30:29,720
why don't you have some tea here?

565
00:30:29,720 --> 00:30:31,590
I'll play a song for you.

566
00:30:31,590 --> 00:30:32,110
No need.

567
00:30:32,270 --> 00:30:33,110
Don't bother.

568
00:30:33,270 --> 00:30:34,100
You go practice your instrument.

569
