Little devil.

573
00:31:20,990 --> 00:31:22,360
No reaction?

574
00:31:27,960 --> 00:31:29,830
Narcissist.

575
00:31:35,690 --> 00:31:37,200
I understand now.

576
00:31:37,390 --> 00:31:38,870
He needs to see my lips

577
00:31:38,900 --> 00:31:41,050
to know what I'm saying.

578
00:31:42,070 --> 00:31:44,790
Little devil, narcissist.

579
00:31:44,820 --> 00:31:46,950
Sadistic monster.

580
00:31:51,320 --> 00:31:51,930
Come back.

581
00:31:53,740 --> 00:31:54,920
Just now...

582
00:31:55,270 --> 00:31:56,280
Young Lord.

583
00:31:56,320 --> 00:31:58,320
Why did the drumbeat suddenly stop?

584
00:32:01,190 --> 00:32:02,750
He can tell I made a mistake with the drums,

585
00:32:02,750 --> 00:32:04,210
but can't hear me speak.

586
00:32:04,470 --> 00:32:06,620
Could it be that he can only hear music?

587
00:32:07,070 --> 00:32:08,810
That's too bizarre.

588
00:32:10,870 --> 00:32:11,790
Young Lord.

589
00:32:11,830 --> 00:32:13,270
You're being unfair.

590
00:32:13,670 --> 00:32:16,750
That sister also made a mistake with her flute just now,

591
00:32:16,830 --> 00:32:18,200
