592
00:32:18,200 --> 00:32:20,000
I didn't notice the flute sound.

593
00:32:20,150 --> 00:32:22,250
I was only focused on your drumming.

594
00:32:40,210 --> 00:32:41,910
I'm sorry, Young Lord.

595
00:32:41,930 --> 00:32:44,430
It turns out that the sister was playing a vertical flute.

596
00:32:44,430 --> 00:32:46,040
I'll continue playing now.

597
00:32:47,100 --> 00:32:47,990
Go ahead.

598
00:33:00,420 --> 00:33:02,150
Unexpectedly,

599
00:33:02,950 --> 00:33:05,550
the Young Lord is actually deaf in both ears.

600
00:33:05,570 --> 00:33:07,290
He has to rely on reading people's lips

601
00:33:07,290 --> 00:33:09,070
to know what they're saying.

602
00:33:14,150 --> 00:33:16,910
But how could he hear my music?

603
00:33:21,900 --> 00:33:24,160
He's quite pitiful when I think about it.

604
00:33:25,200 --> 00:33:27,150
He's so arrogant on a daily basis.

605
00:33:27,440 --> 00:33:29,310
Perhaps it's to cover up

606
00:33:29,310 --> 00:33:31,390
his deep-seated insecurity.

607
00:33:36,790 --> 00:33:38,270
Su Ruofei, wake up!

608
00:33:39,400 --> 00:33:40,470
How can you sympathize

609
00:33:40,470 --> 00:33:42,670
with this little devil who's using you?

610
00:33:45,570 --> 00:33:46,770
There's an assassin!

611
00:33:47,570 --> 00:33:48,460
An assassin?

612
00:33:48,790 --> 00:33:50,120
Why are they here again?

613
00:33:53,600 --> 00:33:54,400
Don't scream,

614
00:33:54,650 --> 00:33:55,640
or I'll kill you.

615
00:33:56,920 --> 00:33:57,810
Great hero,

616
00:33:58,070 --> 00:33:59,150
please spare my life.

617
00:33:59,150 --> 00:34:00,660
If you want money, I don't have a penny.

618
00:34:00,660 --> 00:34:01,510
If you want my body...

619
00:34:01,510 --> 00:34:02,950
I can't offer that either.

620
00:34:02,950 --> 00:34:04,280
Stop talking nonsense.

621
00:34:04,770 --> 00:34:07,500
I know you're Yun Mu's most favored entertainer.

622
00:34:07,670 --> 00:34:09,270
Just tell me Yun Mu's secrets,

623
00:34:09,270 --> 00:34:10,670
and I'll spare your life.

624
