627
00:34:16,630 --> 00:34:18,950
Look, he even makes me live in this storage room.

628
00:34:18,950 --> 00:34:20,510
How can you call that favoritism?

629
00:34:20,510 --> 00:34:21,760
If you want to live, speak up quickly.

630
00:34:21,760 --> 00:34:22,790
Ouch!

631
00:34:22,790 --> 00:34:24,070
I'll tell you!

632
