And he's extremely narcissistic.

636
00:34:31,550 --> 00:34:33,470
He looks in the mirror eight hundred times a day.

637
00:34:33,470 --> 00:34:34,870
He thinks he's the most

638
00:34:34,870 --> 00:34:36,330
handsome man in the world.

639
00:34:38,590 --> 00:34:39,990
I don't want to hear that.

640
00:34:40,030 --> 00:34:41,490
I want to know a more secret

641
