642
00:34:43,760 --> 00:34:44,550
Lethal?

643
00:34:45,310 --> 00:34:48,070
Well, being deaf in both ears should count, right?

644
00:34:48,070 --> 00:34:49,010
Tell me.

645
00:34:49,480 --> 00:34:50,950
Okay.

646
00:34:50,950 --> 00:34:52,430
I'll tell you.

647
00:34:53,630 --> 00:34:55,620
The Young Lord is extremely lecherous.

648
00:34:55,620 --> 00:34:57,790
