649
00:34:57,790 --> 00:34:59,020
but in reality, he's impotent.

650
00:34:59,020 --> 00:35:00,750
He sleeps in his own room every night.

651
00:35:00,750 --> 00:35:02,680
I really don't know anything else.

652
00:35:02,870 --> 00:35:04,360
If that's not enough,

653
00:35:04,510 --> 00:35:05,910
you might as well kill me.

654
00:35:31,160 --> 00:35:31,900
Spare me!

655
00:35:33,730 --> 00:35:34,930
Great hero, please spare my life!

656
00:35:34,930 --> 00:35:36,130
Spare me, great hero!

657
00:35:44,800 --> 00:35:46,060
Oh, it's you.

658
00:35:47,640 --> 00:35:48,900
There was an assassin!

659
00:35:53,430 --> 00:35:55,290
I'm already aware of this matter.

660
00:35:55,980 --> 00:35:57,310
However, by the time I found you,

661
00:35:57,310 --> 00:35:58,990
the assassin had already escaped.

662
00:35:58,990 --> 00:36:00,180
Escaped?

663
00:36:00,550 --> 00:36:01,350
That's right.

664
00:36:03,710 --> 00:36:05,580
How could you let him escape?

665
00:36:06,170 --> 00:36:08,480
Did the assassin say anything to you?

666
00:36:10,220 --> 00:36:11,480
What else could he say?

667
00:36:11,510 --> 00:36:12,990
Wasn't he just after you?

668
00:36:13,630 --> 00:36:15,790
He even forced me to reveal your weakness.

669
00:36:15,790 --> 00:36:18,340
Why am I so unlucky?

670
00:36:18,910 --> 00:36:20,270
He came twice,

671
00:36:20,270 --> 00:36:22,070
and I covered for you both times.

672
00:36:24,210 --> 00:36:26,160
Well, he didn't kill you.

673
00:36:27,110 --> 00:36:29,710
That means you must have revealed my weakness.

674
00:36:31,720 --> 00:36:35,060
How could I possibly reveal your weakness?

675
00:36:35,080 --> 00:36:36,950
I definitely told him righteously that

676
00:36:36,950 --> 00:36:39,630
the Young Lord is unparalleled in this world.

677
00:36:40,220 --> 00:36:41,880
You have no weaknesses at all.

678
00:36:42,140 --> 00:36:43,220
Well said.

679
00:36:43,700 --> 00:36:45,420
I'm indeed unparalleled

680
00:36:45,450 --> 00:36:46,780
and have no weaknesses.

681
00:36:47,070 --> 00:36:49,000
Even if there were any weaknesses,

682
00:36:49,160 --> 00:36:51,600
it's not for a clueless, brainless

683
00:36:51,620 --> 00:36:53,780
entertainer like you to know.

684
00:36:56,300 --> 00:36:57,630
Who says I'm brainless?

685
00:37:00,430 --> 00:37:02,630
You really think you've hidden it well?

686
00:37:03,320 --> 00:37:05,380
It's just that you can't hear, right?

687
00:37:09,680 --> 00:37:11,610
So you've discovered it after all.

688
00:37:13,630 --> 00:37:15,290
Do you know that in this world,

689
00:37:15,390 --> 00:37:17,170
there are two types of people who know this secret?

690
00:37:17,170 --> 00:37:18,030
One type

691
00:37:19,710 --> 00:37:20,670
is my people,

692
00:37:21,320 --> 00:37:22,350
and the other

693
00:37:24,090 --> 00:37:25,170
is dead people.

694
00:37:35,810 --> 00:37:36,750
Young Lord.

695
00:37:37,340 --> 00:37:38,450
I swear.

696
00:37:38,480 --> 00:37:39,750
I am your people.

697
00:37:39,790 --> 00:37:41,800
I am your exclusive entertainer,

698
00:37:42,110 --> 00:37:43,200
one of a kind.

699
00:37:43,640 --> 00:37:45,510
Even when that assassin

700
00:37:45,630 --> 00:37:48,390
held a knife to my throat,

701
00:37:48,410 --> 00:37:49,640
I didn't betray you.

702
00:37:50,660 --> 00:37:52,240
Then why didn't you tell him?

703
00:37:52,240 --> 00:37:55,030
I'm very loyal to my friends.

704
00:37:55,200 --> 00:37:57,180
