708
00:38:03,910 --> 00:38:06,880
However, considering your loyalty,

709
00:38:07,430 --> 00:38:09,100
I'll grant you a new position.

710
00:38:09,580 --> 00:38:10,780
Starting from today,

711
00:38:11,460 --> 00:38:12,830
you'll be my ears.

712
00:38:14,420 --> 00:38:15,510
Ears?

713
00:38:19,860 --> 00:38:21,300
I got it.

714
00:38:21,940 --> 00:38:24,590
Previously, you relied on lip-reading

715
00:38:24,630 --> 00:38:26,830
