716
00:38:26,950 --> 00:38:29,920
But sometimes it's not convenient to do that.

717
00:38:30,070 --> 00:38:33,230
So, I need to use my music

718
00:38:33,260 --> 00:38:34,930
to tell you, right?

719
00:38:36,730 --> 00:38:38,410
As expected of someone I chose.

720
00:38:38,410 --> 00:38:39,850
You catch on quickly.

721
00:38:48,380 --> 00:38:51,230
