723
00:38:54,300 --> 00:38:56,430
If you're willing to help me properly,

724
00:38:56,630 --> 00:38:59,800
I can assist you in re-entering the Symphony Workshop

725
00:38:59,830 --> 00:39:01,690
and restoring your music status.

726
00:39:01,850 --> 00:39:03,220
No way.

727
00:39:04,950 --> 00:39:06,460
Restoring a music status

728
00:39:06,490 --> 00:39:07,850
is a thing of the past.

729
00:39:07,880 --> 00:39:09,610
How can you lump them together?

730
00:39:13,930 --> 00:39:15,200
Then what do you want?

731
00:39:20,930 --> 00:39:23,760
I want my own private chamber.

732
00:39:24,050 --> 00:39:24,660
No way.

733
00:39:25,940 --> 00:39:27,110
As my ears,

734
00:39:27,110 --> 00:39:29,270
you must be with me at all times.

735
00:39:29,520 --> 00:39:30,190
But I...

736
00:39:30,190 --> 00:39:31,380
Think of something practical.

737
00:39:31,380 --> 00:39:34,380
Otherwise, don't blame me for not giving you a chance.

738
00:39:42,360 --> 00:39:43,070
Alright.

739
00:39:52,060 --> 00:39:53,030
Young Lord.

740
00:39:53,320 --> 00:39:55,590
Do you really want to switch beds with me?

741
00:39:55,610 --> 00:39:57,130
I'm afraid the low couch

742
