won't accommodate your noble status.

743
00:40:00,340 --> 00:40:02,300
My bed is specially customized.

744
00:40:02,650 --> 00:40:04,860
It will take some time to transport the new one here.

745
00:40:04,860 --> 00:40:07,700
But you're right about that.

746
00:40:08,220 --> 00:40:11,280
How about I make do and squeeze in with you for a few days?

747
00:40:12,540 --> 00:40:13,670
No need.

748
00:40:14,100 --> 00:40:17,270
You'd better keep your noble status to yourself.

749
00:40:25,860 --> 00:40:27,100
Haitang.

750
00:40:28,280 --> 00:40:30,370
I don't like this scent.

751
00:40:30,510 --> 00:40:31,510
It's too pungent.

752
00:40:31,540 --> 00:40:34,140
Do you have something milder and sweeter?

753
00:40:35,990 --> 00:40:37,820
Change it to chamomile and lily.

754
00:40:38,420 --> 00:40:39,660
Also,

755
00:40:39,690 --> 00:40:41,750
I like Hall crabapples.

756
00:40:41,910 --> 00:40:43,910
Ask someone to plant some in the courtyard for me.

757
00:40:43,910 --> 00:40:45,760
I also like black and red koi fish.

758
00:40:45,760 --> 00:40:48,490
