759
00:40:49,070 --> 00:40:50,070
And...

760
00:40:50,150 --> 00:40:50,950
What else?

761
00:40:55,330 --> 00:40:57,170
That's all for now.

762
00:41:03,440 --> 00:41:04,030
Oh yeah.

763
00:41:05,500 --> 00:41:08,150
There's one more thing I want to ask you.

764
00:41:08,320 --> 00:41:10,840
You can't hear,

765
00:41:10,980 --> 00:41:12,550
so how do you know

766
00:41:12,550 --> 00:41:13,950
what others are playing?

767
00:41:26,910 --> 00:41:28,370
You mean

768
00:41:29,270 --> 00:41:32,190
