769
00:41:32,860 --> 00:41:33,630
Of course.

770
00:41:34,720 --> 00:41:36,360
Since I lost my hearing,

771
00:41:36,560 --> 00:41:38,450
to prevent others from noticing,

772
00:41:38,550 --> 00:41:41,010
