790
00:42:17,550 --> 00:42:19,960
So I investigated at your home

791
00:42:20,250 --> 00:42:22,850
and went through all the ancient medical books

792
00:42:22,990 --> 00:42:24,720
but couldn't find an answer.

793
00:42:25,040 --> 00:42:27,920
Perhaps you were the little ears

794
00:42:27,960 --> 00:42:29,600
sent by heaven to assist me.

795
00:42:29,740 --> 00:42:31,860
