796
00:42:33,370 --> 00:42:36,850
I think it's more like a predestined calamity.

797
00:42:41,590 --> 00:42:44,400
But since you've already mastered

798
00:42:44,440 --> 00:42:47,040
the divine skill of using eyes instead of ears,

799
00:42:47,110 --> 00:42:49,430
why do you still need me to be your ears?

800
00:42:53,350 --> 00:42:54,630
As the Young Lord

801
00:42:54,990 --> 00:42:56,450
