829
00:44:18,130 --> 00:44:19,010
Don't worry.

830
00:44:19,700 --> 00:44:22,320
From now on, I'll be your ears.

831
00:44:22,670 --> 00:44:23,930
If there's any danger,

832
00:44:25,720 --> 00:44:26,910
